---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Bedford Software">
 <main class="min-h-svh min-w-full justify-evenly flex flex-col text-center">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
   <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold md:text-3xl font-serif text-zinc-600">Need a website?</h4>
   <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-7xl font-semibold font-serif leading-6 tracking-tight">Hire local.</h1>
   <p class="w-7/8 mx-auto mt-4 text-[13px]/5 md:text-center md:w-3/5 md:text-base text-zinc-500 font-regular">
    Bedford Software is a website design company located in
    <a class="font-medium underline" href="https://x.com/aarondfrancis" target="_blank">Bedford, Virginia </a>. We build everything from <br /> single-page
    sites to full fledge web applications.
   </p>
   <div class="flex justify-center py-4 md:py-8">
    <form method="POST" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2.5 w-full justify-center" action="#" enctype="multipart/form-data">
     <input
      type="email"
      required=""
      name="email"
      placeholder="Your email"
      class="bg-white/10 rounded-xl border block backdrop-blur-lg px-3 md:px-5 py-1.5 md:py-2.5 text-base md:text-lg placeholder-zinc-500 shadow-lg ring-none outline-none input-style w-full md:w-96 border-1 border-zinc-300/30 focus:border-zinc-400/50"
      autocomplete="off"
     />
     <button
      type="submit"
      class="font-medium rounded-xl bg-green-900 text-zinc-50 hover:bg-green-950 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-zinc-600 px-4 py-2 text-base shadow-xl"
      ><!--[-->Reach Out<!--]--></button
     >
    </form>
   </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-flow-col place-content-center gap-10">
   <div class="relative flex flex-col mt-6 text-zinc-900 bg-zinc-50 shadow-md bg-clip-border rounded-xl w-96">
    <div class="p-6">
     <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="40"
      height="40"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="mb-3"
      ><path d="m15 12-8.373 8.373a1 1 0 1 1-3-3L12 9"></path><path d="m18 15 4-4"></path><path
       d="m21.5 11.5-1.914-1.914A2 2 0 0 1 19 8.172V7l-2.26-2.26a6 6 0 0 0-4.202-1.756L9 2.96l.92.82A6.18 6.18 0 0 1 12 8.4V10l2 2h1.172a2 2 0 0 1 1.414.586L18.5 14.5"
      ></path></svg
     >
     <h5 class="flex mb-2 font-sans text-xl antialiased font-semibold leading-snug tracking-normal text-blue-gray-900">Build</h5>
     <p class="flex text-left font-sans text-base antialiased font-light leading-relaxed text-inherit">
      Using your guidance along with our professional expirence, we work to bring your vision to life.
     </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 pt-0">
     <a href="#" class="inline-block">
      <button
       class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 font-sans text-xs font-bold text-center text-gray-900 uppercase align-middle transition-all rounded-lg select-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:shadow-none disabled:pointer-events-none hover:bg-gray-900/10 active:bg-gray-900/20"
       type="button"
      >
       Learn More
       <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
       </svg>
      </button>
     </a>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="relative flex flex-col mt-6 text-zinc-900 bg-zinc-50 shadow-md bg-clip-border rounded-xl w-96">
    <div class="p-6">
     <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="40"
      height="40"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="mb-3"
      ><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><rect width="20" height="8" x="2" y="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line
       x1="6"
       x2="6.01"
       y1="6"
       y2="6"></line><line x1="6" x2="6.01" y1="18" y2="18"></line></svg
     >
     <h5 class="flex mb-2 font-sans text-xl antialiased font-semibold leading-snug tracking-normal text-blue-gray-900">Host</h5>
     <p class="flex text-left font-sans text-base antialiased font-light leading-relaxed text-inherit">
      We handle it all. From managing your domain to hosting your files on reliable servers. Our services ensure 99% uptime.
     </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 pt-0">
     <a href="#" class="inline-block">
      <button
       class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 font-sans text-xs font-bold text-center text-gray-900 uppercase align-middle transition-all rounded-lg select-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:shadow-none disabled:pointer-events-none hover:bg-gray-900/10 active:bg-gray-900/20"
       type="button"
      >
       Learn More
       <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
       </svg>
      </button>
     </a>
    </div>
   </div>
   <div class="relative flex flex-col mt-6 text-zinc-900 bg-zinc-50 shadow-md bg-clip-border rounded-xl w-96">
    <div class="p-6">
     <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="40"
      height="40"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="mb-3"
      ><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.48 19 2c1 2 2 4.18 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"></path><path
       d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"></path></svg
     >
     <h5 class="flex mb-2 font-sans text-xl antialiased font-semibold leading-snug tracking-normal text-blue-gray-900">Maintain</h5>
     <p class="flex text-left font-sans text-base antialiased font-light leading-relaxed text-inherit">
      Overtime, things might need to be updated or changed. We'll be there, ready to shift things around.
     </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 pt-0">
     <a href="#" class="inline-block">
      <button
       class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 font-sans text-xs font-bold text-center text-gray-900 uppercase align-middle transition-all rounded-lg select-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:shadow-none disabled:pointer-events-none hover:bg-gray-900/10 active:bg-gray-900/20"
       type="button"
      >
       Learn More
       <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3"></path>
       </svg>
      </button>
     </a>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </main>
</Layout>
